---
import { Image } from '@astrojs/image/components';
import Button from '../../Buttons/Button.astro';
---

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="columns">
      <div class="column">
        <h2 class="heading">HydraFacial MD®</h2>
        <p>
          At Body 'N' Bloom, we use the HydraFacial MD® Elite system, which is a
          non-invasive, multistep treatment that combines the benefits of
          next-level hydradermabrasion, a chemical peel, automated painless
          extractions (no pinching!) and special delivery of Antioxidants,
          Hyaluronic Acid, and Peptides that uses Vortex Technology.
        </p>
        <p>
          The HydraFacial MD® treatment is great for all skin types - it is
          highly effective at improving overall skin health like:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Fine Lines and Wrinkles</li>
          <li>Elasticity and Firmness</li>
          <li>Hyperpigmentation/Photo Damage</li>
          <li>Dullness and Dehydration</li>
          <li>Oily/Congested Skin</li>
          <li>Enlarged Pores</li>
          <li>Acne & Blemishes</li>
          <li>Dry or Dehydrated Skin</li>
          <li>Extractions of Black & White Heads</li>
          <li>Exfoliate Dead Skin</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="column">
        <Image
          src="/images/treatments/platelet-rich-plasma/platelet-rich-plasma.jpg"
          alt="A woman who receiving hydrafacial treatment."
          width={600}
          aspectRatio={1 / 1}
          format="webp"
          fit="cover"
          position="center"
          background="transparent"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="columns">
      <div class="column wide">
        <h3>
          The HydraFacial MD® treatment involves the following steps to help
          recharge and renew your skin:
        </h3>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Cleanse and Exfoliate:</strong> dead skin cells are removed,
            and new healthy skin revealed
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Gentle Acid Peel:</strong> loosens impurities from pores without
            irritation
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Extraction:</strong> vortex suction extracts and cleans out pores
            in a painless procedure
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Hydrate:</strong> antioxidants and hyaluronic acid are vortex-fused
            to protect and nourish skin
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="blue-bg">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="columns">
      <div class="column wide">
        <h2 style="">4 REASONS WHY YOU SHOULD HAVE HYDRAFACIAL:</h2>

        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Personalized Treatment, Every Time</strong> - The treatment is
            highly customizable. Everyone has different skin with different needs.
            We can create a treatment that works for you.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong> Fights Acne and Clears Pores</strong> - Adults get acne too,
            though not as often as adolescents do. Hydrafacial is great for everyone,
            especially for people with acne-prone skin. In the third stage of the
            treatment, we will extract all the buildup from deep inside your pores.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Gives Skin a Healthier Appearance</strong> - The anti-oxidant
            treatment in the final stage during Hydrafacial treatment helps the skin
            continue to shine by helping it fight skin cell breakdown and creating
            longer-lasting results.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>No Downtime</strong> - Treatment only takes about one hour and
            causes little to no discomfort.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="columns">
      <div class="column wide">
        <h3>3 Steps to the Best Skin of Your Life.</h3>
        <p>
          The Vortex Fusion Technology works like a vacuum to penetrate inner
          pores and increase the effectiveness of the treatment.
        </p>

        <div class="box">
          <h4>Cleanse</h4>
          <p>
            Deeply cleanses and exfoliates with a gentle peel to uncover a new
            layer of skin.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
          <h4>Extract</h4>
          <p>Remove impurities from pores with painless gentle suction.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
          <h4>Hydrate</h4>
          <p>
            Saturate the skin’s surface with intense moisturizers and
            nourishing, personalized ingredients.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="columns">
      <div class="column wide">
        <h3>Frequently Asked Questions</h3>

        <div class="box">
          <h4>How should I prepare for my appointment?</h4>
          <p>
            Please come makeup free. Please avoid active products such as
            retinols, AHA and BHA for up to 1 week prior. Bring a list of your
            daily skincare products used for your skin care regimen. No waxing
            or shaving of the facial skin for 48 hours prior to your
            appointment. Avoid direct unprotected sun exposure for 48 hours
            prior to your appointment.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
          <h4>
            Can I get a hydrafacial treatment when pregnant/breastfeeding?
          </h4>
          <p>
            Unfortunately not. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, please opt
            for our custom medical facial, where our skin experts tailor a
            facial specifically made for you.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
          <h4>When is a hydrafacial NOT recommended?</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>If you use Accutane – You must wait 6 months to a year</li>
            <li>Active Sunburn</li>
            <li>
              Fillers/ Injections – it is recommended to wait 7-10 days after
              receiving injections.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <div class="" style="margin: 5rem auto 0; display: block;">
            <Button
              text="Book now"
              href="https://bodynbloom.janeapp.com/"
              blank
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
  .blue-bg {
    background-image: var(--soft-blue);
  }

  .box {
    & h4 {
      font-size: 2.6rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
  }
  .container {
    padding: 5rem 10rem;
    max-width: 140rem;
    margin: 0 auto;

    display: flex;
    width: 100%;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      padding: 5rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 400px) {
      padding: 5rem 2rem;
    }

    & h2 {
      font-size: 4rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      text-align: left;

      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        font-size: 3rem;
      }
    }

    & h3 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      text-align: left;
      width: 100%;

      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        font-size: 2.4rem;
      }
    }

    & img {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
    }

    & p {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    & ul {
      margin-left: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;

      & li {
        margin: 1rem 0;
      }
    }
  }

  .columns {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;

    margin-top: 5rem;

    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;

    @media (max-width: 800px) {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    &.short {
      max-width: 80rem;

      & img {
        max-width: 30rem;
      }
    }
  }

  .column {
    & img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
    }

    & video {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      aspect-ratio: 16/9;
    }

    &.row-2 {
      @media (max-width: 800px) {
        grid-row: 2;
      }
    }

    &.wide {
      grid-column: 1 / 3;

      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;

      text-align: left;

      & p {
        width: 100%;
      }

      & ul {
        text-align: left;
        width: 100%;
      }

      @media (max-width: 800px) {
        grid-column: 1 / 2;
      }
    }

    & iframe {
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 16/9;
      margin-bottom: 5rem;
    }

    & p {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
  }

  .heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    text-align: center;

    margin-bottom: 2rem;

    &__container {
      margin-bottom: 5rem;
    }

    & h2 {
      font-size: 4rem;

      text-transform: uppercase;

      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        font-size: 3rem;
      }
    }

    &__accent {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 1rem;

      & img {
        width: 3rem;
      }

      &-line {
        height: 0.1rem;
        width: 6rem;
        background-color: var(--color-blue);
      }
    }
  }
</style>
